                                               nmdc_sfas_brcs:ScientificFocusArea ;
                                      schema1:description """This SFA engineers plant-benefiting microbes for safe and effective deployment in the rhizosphere as plant-promoting probiotics. Research focuses on biocontainment strategies that maintain microbial fitness while enabling secure deployment.
""" ;
