###  https://w3id.org/nmdc/sfas-brcs/microbes_persist
nmdc_sfas_brcs:microbes_persist rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                         nmdc_sfas_brcs:ScientificFocusArea ;
                                schema1:alternateName "Microbes Persist" ;
                                schema1:description """The Microbes Persist SFA aims to understand how microbes shape soil carbon persistence. Using stable isotope-informed approaches, the team characterizes the \"active\" microbiome and virome, scaling from metagenomes to computational models integrating traits at system scale.
